Minimal gear switching=
Using [[Void knight equipment]] or [[Blue moon armour]] can greatly reduce the amount of gear switches required to meet the magic accuracy threshold for killing the elementals. This also makes transitioning from melee to ranged much easier for those getting familiar. 
*Using ranged armour throughout the fight also has the same benefits, as melee armour gives considerably less bonuses to attack. The [[Eclipse atlatl]], which uses melee strength for calculating its maximum hit, is particularly effective for this approach as it requires fewer compromises on melee strength and ranged accuracy.

In order to determine which gear to use, it is important to look at the magic attack bonus of the total gear chosen.
<br/><br/>
