=== High Level / Resetting ===
When fighting the Titans in a duo with high end gear and high stats, damage taken from elementals per kill is very low. It is possible to forego use of fire and water spells for the elementals, and rely on [[thralls]], especially if resetting health, prayer, and special attack energy between kills at the [[Nardah statue]] or an [[ornate rejuvenation pool]]. This strategy is most effective for maximizing kills-per-hour, although the gear threshold required to execute this strategy is reasonably high.

If you instead opt for standard spells to kill elementals and remove barriers, reaching a magic attack bonus of a minimum of 70 is required. The most effective switches to reach this threshold are typically magic armour and a staff, with expensive gear such as [[ancestral robes]] / [[virtus robes]] (+61) only providing a modest accuracy boost over armour such as [[Ahrim's equipment]] (+52). If using [[amulet of rancour]] (-6) or [[ferocious gloves]] (-16), swapping to [[occult necklace]] (+12) / [[amulet of fury]] (+10) and [[barrows gloves]] (+6) / [[tormented bracelet]] (+10) might be required to hit +70 magic attack bonus.
